Name:                   core-haskell
Cabal-Version:          >= 1.14
License:                BSD3
License-file:           LICENSE
Category:               Language, Compilers/Interpreters
Version:                0.6.2
Build-Type:             Simple
Synopsis:               A subset of Haskell using in UCC for teaching purpose
